---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — PhoneHub"
  description="PhoneHub is a free product comparison platform helping users find, compare, and decide on phones, laptops, cars, and more."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">About PhoneHub</h1>

    <div class="glass-card p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        PhoneHub is a <span class="text-white font-semibold">free product comparison platform</span> helping users find, compare, and decide on phones, laptops, cars, tablets, smartwatches, TVs, cameras, and more. We aggregate specifications from multiple sources, generate AI-powered reviews, and provide price comparisons with affiliate links to help you make informed purchase decisions.
      </p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">What We Do</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Aggregate Specs</strong> — We collect detailed product specifications from GSMArena, Wikidata, manufacturer websites, and other open sources to build comprehensive product profiles.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">AI-Powered Reviews</strong> — Our AI analyzes specs and user feedback to generate honest, balanced reviews highlighting pros and cons for each product.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Side-by-Side Comparison</strong> — Compare up to 4 products at once with our interactive comparison table, highlighting which product leads in each spec category.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Price Tracking</strong> — We aggregate prices from Amazon, Flipkart, and other retailers so you can find the best deal.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span><strong class="text-gray-200">Tech News</strong> — Stay up to date with the latest tech news aggregated from top publications like The Verge, Android Authority, TechCrunch, and more.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data Sources</h2>
        <p>
          Product data on PhoneHub is sourced from <span class="text-accent-blue">GSMArena</span>, <span class="text-accent-blue">Wikidata</span>, manufacturer websites, and other publicly available databases. We strive for accuracy, but specifications may occasionally contain errors. If you spot incorrect information, please let us know through our <a href="/phonehub/contact" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">AI-Generated Content Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          Some content on PhoneHub, including product reviews and summaries, is generated with the assistance of artificial intelligence. While we strive for accuracy and fairness, AI-generated content may contain errors, omissions, or biases. We recommend verifying critical information from multiple sources before making purchase decisions. AI-generated reviews represent our analysis and should not be considered as professional endorsements or criticisms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Coverage</h2>
        <p>
          With over <span class="text-white font-semibold">1,400+ products</span> spanning phones, laptops, cars, tablets, smartwatches, TVs, and cameras, PhoneHub covers a wide range of categories and brands to help you research and decide with confidence.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-white/5 text-xs text-gray-500">
        <p>PhoneHub is an independent project and is not affiliated with any product manufacturer or retailer.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
